Package: wUMAP
Title: PC-Distance Modification for UMAP in Seurat Objects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Lachlan", "Dryburgh", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lachlan.dryburgh@example.com")
Description: Tools for modifying the PC-space distance used as input to UMAP
    in Seurat workflows. Includes heuristic global PC-axis weighting
    (RunWeightedUMAP(), RunWeightedNeighbors()), a principled noise-PC filter
    based on the Marchenko-Pastur law (mp.filter), and a geometrically
    motivated local PCA distance metric (RunLocalPCAUMAP(),
    RunLocalPCANeighbors()) that measures cell–neighbour distances in a
    locally-fitted PCA basis. Whether any modification improves results is
    dataset-dependent; a benchmark vignette evaluates all approaches against
    an independent ground truth.
